him the papers. I can't imagine.

91
00:10:52,652 --> 00:10:54,552
Look...

92
00:10:54,654 --> 00:10:57,646
- We don't need to go over this.
Just issue the papers.
- [Knocking]

93
00:10:57,757 --> 00:10:59,657
- [Clicks Fingers]
- Come here.

94
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:02,990
Look, I can't talk anymore about it.
I have a client in front of me.

95
00:11:03,095 --> 00:11:06,656
Just a second. Okay?
I'll be right with you.

96
00:11:06,766 --> 00:11:09,997
Okay. I'll call you back at 2:00.
Sounds good.

97
00:11:11,504 --> 00:11:14,735
So. Where is that?
Oh, here it is.

98
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,707
- How have you been doin'?
- Pretty good, I guess.

99
00:11:17,810 --> 00:11:21,075
That's good.
Did they take the monitor off?

100
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:23,580
Yeah, they came
and got it this morning.

101
00:11:23,683 --> 00:11:26,982
You know, I hope this experience has
changed your life in some way.

102
00:11:27,086 --> 00:11:31,079
Rick, you are facing 20 years.

103
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:34,523
Twenty big ones.

104
00:11:34,627 --> 00:11:40,031
But bein' the person I am, I pulled some
strings so they would go easy on you.

105
00:11:40,132 --> 00:11:42,965
I mean, I don't know
what you're thinkin' about.

106
00:11:43,069 --> 00:11:46,038
I mean, you're a young black man.
You have a lot of potential.

107
00:11:46,138 --> 00:11:49,198
You don't deserve to be locked
in some cage like an animal.

108
00:11:49,308 --> 00:11:53,904
No black man deserves that.
That's what they want.

109
00:11:54,013 --> 00:11:57,949
You can't take this stuff for granted.

110
00:11:58,050 --> 00:12:00,746
[Sighs Deeply]

111
00:12:00,853 --> 00:12:04,414
I put my name on the line
for you today.

112
00:12:04,523 --> 00:12:08,015
So when you go out there
in that free world...

113
00:12:08,127 --> 00:12:11,119
and you're not worryin'
about time passin' by...

114
00:12:11,230 --> 00:12:15,690
or checking in,
you just remember Mrs. Martin.

115
00:12:15,801 --> 00:12:20,966
You remember. I was the one
who kept you out of prison.

116
00:12:21,841 --> 00:12:24,708
And you know what, Rick?

117
00:12:24,810 --> 00:12:29,907
If you just think about
getting in any trouble...

118
00:12:30,015 --> 00:12:32,916
I'll put you back in there.

119
00:12:33,018 --> 00:12:38,081
- I will. Read my lips.
- [Phone Ringing]

120
00:12:38,190 --> 00:12:42,286
