122
00:12:48,634 --> 00:12:51,535
[Rings]

123
00:12:54,306 --> 00:12:56,433
[Rings]

124
00:12:56,542 --> 00:12:59,136
[Sighs]
Just gotta believe in yourself.

125
00:12:59,245 --> 00:13:01,907
[Rings]

126
00:13:02,014 --> 00:13:06,212
I do. You wouldn't believe
how much I do, Mrs. Martin.

127
00:13:06,318 --> 00:13:09,344
And I know it's hard when I come here
every day with the same attitude...

128
00:13:09,455 --> 00:13:11,753
like I don't appreciate nothin'.

129
00:13:11,857 --> 00:13:13,722
I appreciate everything
you've done for me.

130
00:13:13,826 --> 00:13:15,726
I know if it weren't for you,
I probably would have been...

131
00:13:15,828 --> 00:13:21,733
violated this probation, or I'd still be
in the streets doin'the same old things.

132
00:13:21,834 --> 00:13:23,961
Just wanted to let you know
I'm very thankful.

133
00:13:26,038 --> 00:13:29,530
And also, goin'back tojail, that's
the last thing I got on my mind.

134
00:13:29,642 --> 00:13:31,837
You can count on that.

135
00:13:31,944 --> 00:13:35,243
You know, that's just
what I wanted to hear.

136
00:13:35,347 --> 00:13:38,043
I mean, that just
makes me so proud.

137
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:40,914
Well, good luck.

138
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:43,648
- Thanks, Mrs. Martin.
- Thank you.

139
00:13:46,325 --> 00:13:48,350
[Rick Narrating]
That's my man D-Mo.

140
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:51,429
