I just came from Baltimore last week,
man. Nigga just cut out, man.

146
00:14:06,278 --> 00:14:09,179
- What?
- Word up. Claim I'm two-timin' his head.

147
00:14:09,281 --> 00:14:11,112
Don't tell me
he ain't got my money.

148
00:14:11,217 --> 00:14:14,880
- Oh.
- For real, though, it was only a "G".

149
00:14:14,987 --> 00:14:17,421
- A "G"? I think I'd have
hit that nigga too.
- Still, man.

150
00:14:17,523 --> 00:14:20,390
- What's goin' on, man?
