151
00:14:20,492 --> 00:14:23,484
But look, man. I been wantin'
to holler at you anyway, right?

152
00:14:23,596 --> 00:14:26,565
- Mm-hmm.
- Look, man.

153
00:14:26,665 --> 00:14:29,498
I'm ready to step my game up.

154
00:14:29,602 --> 00:14:32,730
I'm tired of slingin' these sixty-twos
and these eighties.

155
00:14:32,838 --> 00:14:34,806
That shit just ain't
doin' enough for me.

156
00:14:34,907 --> 00:14:37,341
I'm ready to make me
some real money.

157
00:14:37,443 --> 00:14:41,470
Mm. Yo. You know that's
a whole 'nother gig, man.

158
00:14:41,580 --> 00:14:44,811
- I hear you.
- Man, you see this little
street shit we used to...

159
00:14:44,917 --> 00:14:47,147
- back in the days, man, you know?
- Mm-hmm.

160
00:14:47,253 --> 00:14:51,713
Gotta have your clientele, man,
you gotta know how to move it,
you gotta be smart about it.

161
00:14:51,824 --> 00:14:53,985
And besides, you can't
do this shit by yourself.

162
00:14:54,093 --> 00:14:55,993
Look, man.

163
00:14:56,095 --> 00:15:00,054
