this whole city down.

165
00:15:02,334 --> 00:15:05,735
Look, all we need is the starter keys,
baby, and that's it.

166
00:15:05,838 --> 00:15:08,568
That's all from there.
That's it.

167
00:15:12,011 --> 00:15:14,479
A'ight. Tell you what
I'm gonna do then.

168
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:18,038
You know you my man. Your shit
always been tight all the time.

169
00:15:18,150 --> 00:15:21,017
We'll go up top.
Go check my piece.

170
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:23,554
If everything a'ight
up there when I get back...

171
00:15:23,656 --> 00:15:26,386
I come back here in about a week or two.
We'll come check you.

172
00:15:26,492 --> 00:15:28,551
- We could rock. That's cool?
- All right.

173
00:15:28,661 --> 00:15:30,993
- That's cool.
- All right, man.

174
00:15:31,096 --> 00:15:33,064
[D-Mo, Narrating]
Now all I had to do...

175
00:15:33,165 --> 00:15:35,998
