feel a li'l bit more confident.

179
00:15:49,715 --> 00:15:53,879
Huh. I told Kenny Drama had
Southeast on the lock.

180
00:15:53,986 --> 00:15:56,284
Man, that was some bullshit.

181
00:15:56,388 --> 00:15:58,618
Drama straight outta Northeast.
Lincoln Heights.

182
00:15:58,724 --> 00:16:01,784
He don't even know
how to hustle.

183
00:16:01,894 --> 00:16:05,125
