come from stickin'up crap games.

184
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:07,357
Or breakin'in nigga's cars
at the Go-Go.

185
00:16:07,466 --> 00:16:10,833
Stealin'they guns.
Sellin' 'em to other dudes.

186
00:16:10,936 --> 00:16:13,461
But if I could get him
to follow my lead...

187
00:16:13,572 --> 00:16:16,200
[Chuckles] the young 'un would
be down with the program.

188
00:16:17,643 --> 00:16:20,669
What's up?

189
00:16:20,779 --> 00:16:24,738
Look, right? I don't even like bein'
here. I wanna make this quick.

190
00:16:24,850 --> 00:16:27,819
Look, I know you and your moms kinda
been hurtin' for money, right?

191
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:30,753
- Yeah.
- But I was hollerin' at my man
from Houston last night.

192
00:16:30,856 --> 00:16:33,222
He talkin' about puttin' us on,
helpin' us make some real money.

193
00:16:33,325 --> 00:16:38,558
- Some real money, man.
- I ain't about sellin' no drugs.

194
00:16:38,664 --> 00:16:40,825
Ain't no drug dealer,
I'm a thug, nigga.

195
00:16:40,933 --> 00:16:43,094
It's better than this robbin'
and stealin' you doin'.

196
00:16:43,202 --> 00:16:47,002
- It pay my bills.
- You ain't makin' no real money.

197
00:16:47,106 --> 00:16:50,564
You can't honestly tell me you happy with
the way you livin'. Look at this, man.

198
00:16:50,676 --> 00:16:52,769
Come on. Look.

199
