213
00:17:40,192 --> 00:17:43,787
- I don't know, man.
- Look, man. Look.

214
00:17:43,896 --> 00:17:46,126
It ain't hard.
This shit is easy, man.

215
00:17:46,231 --> 00:17:48,631
Look, man, I...

216
00:17:48,734 --> 00:17:51,931
- All I can say is, I'll try, man.
- That's all I'm askin'.

217
00:17:52,037 --> 00:17:56,064
- A'ight, I'm down for whatever, dog.
- A'ight, bad.

